<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>Fortinet Clipboard Bookmarklets</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #f5efe4;
        --panel: rgba(255, 252, 245, 0.8);
        --panel-strong: #fffaf0;
        --text: #1f2937;
        --muted: #5b6472;
        --accent: #0f766e;
        --accent-strong: #115e59;
        --accent-soft: rgba(15, 118, 110, 0.12);
        --border: rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.12);
        --shadow: 0 18px 50px rgba(31, 41, 55, 0.12);
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        font-family: "Avenir Next", "Segoe UI", sans-serif;
        color: var(--text);
        background:
          radial-gradient(circle at top left, rgba(234, 179, 8, 0.22), transparent 34%),
          radial-gradient(circle at top right, rgba(14, 165, 233, 0.2), transparent 28%),
          linear-gradient(180deg, #fffaf1 0%, var(--bg) 100%);
      }

      main {
        width: min(980px, calc(100% - 32px));
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 48px 0 64px;
      }

      .hero {
        padding: 32px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        border-radius: 28px;
        background: var(--panel);
        backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .eyebrow {
        margin: 0 0 12px;
        font-size: 0.78rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.14em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--accent-strong);
      }

      h1 {
        margin: 0;
        font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 6vw, 4.3rem);
        line-height: 0.96;
        letter-spacing: -0.05em;
      }

      .lead {
        max-width: 56ch;
        margin: 18px 0 0;
        font-size: 1.06rem;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .intro {
        margin-top: 22px;
        padding: 18px 20px;
        border-radius: 20px;
        background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.9);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .intro p {
        margin: 0;
        line-height: 1.7;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      .steps {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(180px, 1fr));
        gap: 14px;
        margin: 28px 0 0;
        padding: 0;
        list-style: none;
      }

      .steps li {
        padding: 16px 18px;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: var(--panel-strong);
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
      }

      .steps strong,
      .card h2 {
        display: block;
        margin-bottom: 6px;
      }

      .grid {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
        gap: 18px;
        margin-top: 28px;
      }

      .card {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        gap: 14px;
        padding: 22px;
        border-radius: 24px;
        border: 1px solid var(--border);
        background: rgba(255, 250, 240, 0.92);
        box-shadow: var(--shadow);
      }

      .card p {
        margin: 0;
        color: var(--muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }

      .bookmarklet {
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        min-height: 52px;
        padding: 0 18px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--accent) 0%, #0ea5e9 100%);
        color: white;
        text-decoration: none;
        font-weight: 700;
        letter-spacing: 0.01em;
        box-shadow: 0 12px 24px rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.22);
      }

      .bookmarklet:hover,
      .bookmarklet:focus-visible {
        transform: translateY(-1px);
        box-shadow: 0 16px 28px rgba(14, 116, 144, 0.28);
      }

      .hint {
        margin-top: 14px;
        padding: 14px 16px;
        border-left: 4px solid var(--accent);
        border-radius: 14px;
        background: var(--accent-soft);
        color: var(--text);
      }

      .subtle {
        margin-top: 10px;
        color: var(--muted);
      }

      code {
        padding: 2px 6px;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
        font-size: 0.88rem;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        main {
          width: min(100% - 20px, 980px);
          padding-top: 20px;
        }

        .hero,
        .card {
          padding: 20px;
          border-radius: 22px;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <p class="eyebrow">Fortinet SSL VPN Clipboard</p>
        <h1>Skip the repetitive Fortinet clipboard clicks.</h1>
        <p class="lead">
          These bookmarklets automate the clipboard panel inside the Fortinet SSL-VPN
          web UI. Save them once, then use a single click instead of stepping through
          the same clipboard flow every time.
        </p>
        <div class="intro">
          <p>
            The manual process is usually: press <code>F8</code>, open
            <code>Clipboard</code>, request or paste text, press the copy button, press
            <code>Clear</code>, and close the slideover. These bookmarklets take care of
            the repeated clipboard actions for you while that Fortinet page is open.
          </p>
        </div>
        <ol class="steps">
          <li><strong>1. Install them</strong>Drag each button below to your bookmarks bar once.</li>
          <li><strong>2. Open Fortinet</strong>Keep your current Fortinet SSL-VPN page open in the browser.</li>
          <li><strong>3. Click once</strong>Press <code>↑ Send clipboard</code> or <code>↓ Get VPN clipboard</code> whenever you need it.</li>
        </ol>
      </section>

      <section class="grid" aria-label="Bookmarklets">
        <% bookmarklets.forEach((bookmarklet) => { %>
          <article class="card">
            <h2><%= bookmarklet.name %></h2>
            <p><%= bookmarklet.description %></p>
            <div>
              <a class="bookmarklet" href="<%- bookmarklet.href %>"><%= bookmarklet.name %></a>
            </div>
            <p><code><%= bookmarklet.id %>.js</code></p>
          </article>
        <% }); %>
      </section>

      <p class="hint">
        If the browser asks for clipboard permission, allow it for the Fortinet page.
        The <code>↑ Send clipboard</code> bookmarklet needs clipboard read access.
      </p>
      <p class="subtle">
        <code>↑ Send clipboard</code> moves text from your computer into the remote
        session. <code>↓ Get VPN clipboard</code> brings the remote clipboard back to
        your local machine.
      </p>
    </main>
  </body>
</html>
